        |         |                     | that might be an error, but could also happen   |        |
        |         |                     | when running a script normally                  |        |
        --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        | 5       | E_CORE_ERROR        | Fatal errors that occur during PHP's initial    | 16     |
        |         |                     | start-up                                        |        |
        --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
